,"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-12-03T09:28:25Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Financial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8478115b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Human Resources Director is accountable for defining and implementing the High Speed Two (HS2) People Strategy. They ensure that HS2’s operating model, and supplier and other stakeholder relationships, provide the agile, performance driven, and effective organisation needed to achieve the challenging targets and timelines of the programme.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-11T09:55:53Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief People Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84781b5c-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>​The Chief Executive Officer has overall responsibility for the development and delivery of the High Speed Two (<abbr title=\"High Speed Two\">HS2</abbr>) project, and the growth of ​<abbr title=\"High Speed Two\">HS2</abbr> Ltd.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-03-02T16:08:34Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84781c01-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-05-23T11:51:46Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Managing Director, Rail Development","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ebcdce3a-b241-4a3e-94d5-f7431243c680","details":{"body":"<p>The Safety and Assurance Director leads on the vision and direction for health, safety and security at High Speed Two (<abbr title=\"High Speed Two\">HS2</abbr>) Limited. The health, safety and security of the workforce in construction and operation, and the safety of passengers and lineside neighbours, is their first and ongoing consideration. They will provide the integrated management approach and risk controls for <abbr title=\"Health, Safety, Security and Environmental\">HSSE</abbr> across the <abbr title=\"High Speed Two\">HS2</abbr> Ltd organisation and its operations.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-11T09:56:58Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Railway Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"34137da4-6259-431a-bd1e-5d9ea77df18b","details":{"body":"<p>The General Counsel and Company Secretary is responsible for all of High Speed Two (<abbr title=\"High Speed Two\">HS2</abbr>)’s legal requirements. This includes governance/delegations regime and related administration (running the Board and its sub-committees, and the Executive and its sub-committees).</p>\n\n<p>Additional responsibilities include Companies House filings and the anti-fraud/ethics function, all with a focus on delivering value for money for the taxpayer.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-02-18T09:40:22Z","schema_name":"role","title":"General Counsel","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"1fb521f9-668a-4893-a05a-4ae52b45657e","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-26T14:30:55Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Delivery Director - Stations","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7f3a104a-8546-4bcd-aa28-497e63a678a3","details":{"body":"<p>Community engagement and communications</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-08-16T10:00:57Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Strategic Director Community Engagement and Communications","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ee29f661-63e4-4ac7-8493-107fa9499d5e","details":{"body":"<p>The Delivery Director for Phase One will play a key role in leading and developing the detailed design of the new construction directorate.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-23T13:49:15Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Civils Delivery Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"cc4c1077-caf8-40aa-bec5-63a5c7893a73","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-08-16T15:18:01Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Technical Services Delivery Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"f773db1c-9135-47e3-b00e-939a0ddddaef","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-11T10:15:03Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Delivery Director - Railway Systems","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"a4ddb0a8-f871-44bc-b371-7152a626b54a","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-08-16T15:24:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Commercial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"a25b2905-c47e-44cf-b138-e1ba5cd94dac","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-06-23T10:34:03Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Phase 2a Delivery Director ","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"3783d4e9-2135-4053-aeec-d9e05b88bb31","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-09-09T14:02:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c4502e2e-0002-468a-a016-6b40199c92fb","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-11T10:18:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Deputy Chair","withdr